    "In the feedback group, the Multiple R increased slightly to 0.889, with the R-Square rising to 79%, demonstrating a slightly stronger relationship between engagement and score improvements.",
    "Interestingly, the feedback group experienced a larger increase in the effect of motivation than engagement, as reflected by the more pronounced improvement in R-Square values for motivation.",
    "These findings suggest that AI-generated feedback has a greater influence on motivation compared to engagement, amplifying the motivational benefits of the revision process to a greater extent.",
